    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Culture and period of ancient nomadic people who formed a state in Mongolia north of the empire of the Han Dynasty. What little is known of the culture is offered by Chinese literary sources and a few archaeological sites and artifacts.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
